21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_hip(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 dns_name_t name;
25 isc_buffer_t buffer;
26 isc_buffer_t hit_len;
27 isc_buffer_t key_len;
28 unsigned char *start;
29 size_t len;
30
31 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_hip);
32
33 UNUSED(type);
34 UNUSED(rdclass);
35 UNUSED(callbacks);
36
37 /*
38 * Dummy HIT len.
39 */
40 hit_len = *target;
41 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(0, target));
42
43 /*
44 * Algorithm.
45 */
46 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
47 false));
48 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
49 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
50 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
51
52 /*
53 * Dummy KEY len.
54 */
55 key_len = *target;
56 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(0, target));
57
58 /*
59 * HIT (base16).
60 */
61 start = isc_buffer_used(target);
62 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
63 false));
64 RETTOK(isc_hex_decodestring(DNS_AS_STR(token), target));
65
66 /*
67 * Fill in HIT len.
68 */
69 len = (unsigned char *)isc_buffer_used(target) - start;
70 if (len > 0xffU)
71 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
72 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer((uint32_t)len, &hit_len));
73
74 /*
75 * Public key (base64).
76 */
77 start = isc_buffer_used(target);
78 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
79 false));
80 RETTOK(isc_base64_decodestring(DNS_AS_STR(token), target));
81
82 /*
83 * Fill in KEY len.
84 */
85 len = (unsigned char *)isc_buffer_used(target) - start;
86 if (len > 0xffffU)
87 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
88 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer((uint32_t)len, &key_len));
89
90 if (origin == NULL)
91 origin = dns_rootname;
92
93 /*
94 * Rendezvous Servers.
95 */
96 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
97 do {
98 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
99 isc_tokentype_string,
100 true));
101 if (token.type != isc_tokentype_string)
102 break;
103 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
104 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options,
105 target));
106 } while (1);
107
108 /*
109 * Let upper layer handle eol/eof.
110 */
111 isc_lex_ungettoken(lexer, &token);
112
113 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
114}

116static inline isc_result_t
117totext_hip(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
118 isc_region_t region;
119 dns_name_t name;
120 unsigned int length, key_len, hit_len;
121 unsigned char algorithm;
122 char buf[sizeof("225 ")];
123
124 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_hip);
125 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
126
127 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
128
129 hit_len = uint8_fromregion(&region);
130 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
131
132 algorithm = uint8_fromregion(&region);
133 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
134
135 key_len = uint16_fromregion(&region);
136 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
137
138 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
139 RETERR(str_totext("( ", target));
140
141 /*
142 * Algorithm
143 */
144 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", algorithm);
145 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
146
147 /*
148 * HIT.
149 */
150 INSIST(hit_len < region.length);
151 length = region.length;
152 region.length = hit_len;
153 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&region, 1, "", target));
154 region.length = length - hit_len;
155 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
156
157 /*
158 * Public KEY.
159 */
160 INSIST(key_len <= region.length);
161 length = region.length;
162 region.length = key_len;
163 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&region, 1, "", target));
164 region.length = length - key_len;
165 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
166
167 /*
168 * Rendezvous Servers.
169 */
170 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
171 while (region.length > 0) {
172 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
173
174 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&name, false, target));
175 isc_region_consume(&region, name.length);
176 if (region.length > 0)
177 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
178 }
179 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
180 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
181 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
182}

184static inline isc_result_t
185fromwire_hip(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
186 isc_region_t region, rr;
187 dns_name_t name;
188 uint8_t hit_len;
189 uint16_t key_len;
190
191 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_hip);
192
193 UNUSED(type);
194 UNUSED(rdclass);
195
196 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &region);
197 if (region.length < 4U)
198 RETERR(DNS_R_FORMERR);
199
200 rr = region;
201 hit_len = uint8_fromregion(&region);
202 if (hit_len == 0)
203 RETERR(DNS_R_FORMERR);
204 isc_region_consume(&region, 2); /* hit length + algorithm */
205 key_len = uint16_fromregion(&region);
206 if (key_len == 0)
207 RETERR(DNS_R_FORMERR);
208 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
209 if (region.length < (unsigned) (hit_len + key_len))
210 RETERR(DNS_R_FORMERR);
211
212 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, rr.base, 4 + hit_len + key_len));
213 isc_buffer_forward(source, 4 + hit_len + key_len);
214
215 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
216 while (isc_buffer_activelength(source) > 0) {
217 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
218 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
219 }
220 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
221}

223static inline isc_result_t
224towire_hip(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
225 isc_region_t region;
226
227 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_hip);
228 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
229
230 UNUSED(cctx);
231
232 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
233 return (mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
234}

236static inline int
237compare_hip(ARGS_COMPARE) {
238 isc_region_t region1;
239 isc_region_t region2;
240
241 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
242 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
243 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_hip);
244 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
245 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
246
247 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
248 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
249 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
250}

252static inline isc_result_t
253fromstruct_hip(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
254 dns_rdata_hip_t *hip = source;
255 dns_rdata_hip_t myhip;
256 isc_result_t result;
257
258 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_hip);
259 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
260 REQUIRE(hip->common.rdtype == type);
261 REQUIRE(hip->common.rdclass == rdclass);
262 REQUIRE(hip->hit_len > 0 && hip->hit != NULL);
263 REQUIRE(hip->key_len > 0 && hip->key != NULL);
264 REQUIRE((hip->servers == NULL && hip->servers_len == 0) ||
265 (hip->servers != NULL && hip->servers_len != 0));
266
267 UNUSED(type);
268 UNUSED(rdclass);
269
270 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(hip->hit_len, target));
271 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(hip->algorithm, target));
272 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(hip->key_len, target));
273 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, hip->hit, hip->hit_len));
274 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, hip->key, hip->key_len));
275
276 myhip = *hip;
277 for (result = dns_rdata_hip_first(&myhip);
278 result == ISC_R_SUCCESS;
279 result = dns_rdata_hip_next(&myhip))
280 /* empty */;
281
282 return(mem_tobuffer(target, hip->servers, hip->servers_len));
283}

285static inline isc_result_t
286tostruct_hip(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
287 isc_region_t region;
288 dns_rdata_hip_t *hip = target;
289
290 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_hip);
291 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
292 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
293
294 hip->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
295 hip->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
296 ISC_LINK_INIT(&hip->common, link);
297
298 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
299
300 hip->hit_len = uint8_fromregion(&region);
301 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
302
303 hip->algorithm = uint8_fromregion(&region);
304 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
305
306 hip->key_len = uint16_fromregion(&region);
307 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
308
309 hip->hit = hip->key = hip->servers = NULL;
310
311 hip->hit = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, hip->hit_len);
312 if (hip->hit == NULL)
313 goto cleanup;
314 isc_region_consume(&region, hip->hit_len);
315
316 INSIST(hip->key_len <= region.length);
317
318 hip->key = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, hip->key_len);
319 if (hip->key == NULL)
320 goto cleanup;
321 isc_region_consume(&region, hip->key_len);
322
323 hip->servers_len = region.length;
324 if (hip->servers_len != 0) {
325 hip->servers = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, region.length);
326 if (hip->servers == NULL)
327 goto cleanup;
328 }
329
330 hip->offset = hip->servers_len;
331 hip->mctx = mctx;
332 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
333
334 cleanup:
335 if (hip->hit != NULL)
336 isc_mem_free(mctx, hip->hit);
337 if (hip->key != NULL)
338 isc_mem_free(mctx, hip->key);
339 if (hip->servers != NULL)
340 isc_mem_free(mctx, hip->servers);
341 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
342
343}
344
345static inline void
346freestruct_hip(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
347 dns_rdata_hip_t *hip = source;
348
349 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
350
351 if (hip->mctx == NULL)
352 return;
353
354 isc_mem_free(hip->mctx, hip->hit);
355 isc_mem_free(hip->mctx, hip->key);
356 if (hip->servers != NULL)
357 isc_mem_free(hip->mctx, hip->servers);
358 hip->mctx = NULL;
359}

406
407isc_result_t
408dns_rdata_hip_first(dns_rdata_hip_t *hip) {
409 if (hip->servers_len == 0)
410 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
411 hip->offset = 0;
412 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
413}
414
415isc_result_t
416dns_rdata_hip_next(dns_rdata_hip_t *hip) {
417 isc_region_t region;
418 dns_name_t name;
419
420 if (hip->offset >= hip->servers_len)
421 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
422
423 region.base = hip->servers + hip->offset;
424 region.length = hip->servers_len - hip->offset;
425 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
426 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
427 hip->offset += name.length;
428 INSIST(hip->offset <= hip->servers_len);
429 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
430}
431
432void
433dns_rdata_hip_current(dns_rdata_hip_t *hip, dns_name_t *name) {
434 isc_region_t region;
435
436 REQUIRE(hip->offset < hip->servers_len);
437
438 region.base = hip->servers + hip->offset;
439 region.length = hip->servers_len - hip->offset;
440 dns_name_fromregion(name, &region);
441
442 INSIST(name->length + hip->offset <= hip->servers_len);
443}

445static inline int
446casecompare_hip(ARGS_COMPARE) {
447 isc_region_t r1;
448 isc_region_t r2;
449 dns_name_t name1;
450 dns_name_t name2;
451 int order;
452 uint8_t hit_len;
453 uint16_t key_len;
454
455 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
456 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
457 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_hip);
458 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
459 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
460
461 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
462 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
463
464 INSIST(r1.length > 4);
465 INSIST(r2.length > 4);
466 order = memcmp(r1.base, r2.base, 4);
467 if (order != 0)
468 return (order);
469
470 hit_len = uint8_fromregion(&r1);
471 isc_region_consume(&r1, 2); /* hit length + algorithm */
472 key_len = uint16_fromregion(&r1);
473 isc_region_consume(&r1, 2); /* key length */
474 isc_region_consume(&r2, 4);
475
476 INSIST(r1.length >= (unsigned) (hit_len + key_len));
477 INSIST(r2.length >= (unsigned) (hit_len + key_len));
478 order = memcmp(r1.base, r2.base, hit_len + key_len);
479 if (order != 0)
480 return (order);
481 isc_region_consume(&r1, hit_len + key_len);
482 isc_region_consume(&r2, hit_len + key_len);
483
484 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
485 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
486 while (r1.length != 0 && r2.length != 0) {
487 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &r1);
488 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &r2);
489 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
490 if (order != 0)
491 return (order);
492
493 isc_region_consume(&r1, name_length(&name1));
494 isc_region_consume(&r2, name_length(&name2));
495 }
496 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
497}
